<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>PublicHealthCenter Recommendation System</title>
    <!--부트스트랩 css 추가-->
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" integrity="sha384-GLhlTQ8iRABdZLl6O3oVMWSktQOp6b7In1Zl3/Jr59b6EGGoI1aFkw7cmDA6j6gD" crossorigin="anonymous">

    <style>
        img {
            margin: 0 0 5px;
            width: 70%;
            height: 550px;
        }


        .list{
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .list .card-contain{
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            margin: 10px;
        }
        .list .card-contain .card {
            width: 900px;
        }

        .header {
            padding-top: 30px;
            font-size: 37px;
            font-weight: bold;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: black;
        }

    </style>
</head>
<body>
<div class="header">
    <p>PublicHealthCenter Recommendation Result</p>
</div>
    <div class="list">
        {{#each outputFormList}}
        <div class="card-contain">
            <div class="card">
                <h5 class="card-header">
                    <div style="display: flex">
                        <h5 class="card-title">{{publicHealthCenterName}} </h5>
                        <p>({{distance}})</p>
                    </div>
                </h5>
                <div class="card-body">

                    <div style="display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items: center;">
                        <div style="display: block;">
                            <p class="card-text">{{publicHealthCenterAddress}}</p>
                            <p style="color: gray">반경 10km 내에 가까운 보건소의 위치 최대 3곳 추천 리스트입니다.</p>
                        </div>

                        <div style="display: flex; margin-left: auto; " >
                            <a href="{{directionUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary" style="margin-right: 10px; height: 40px;">지도 보기</a>
                            <a href="{{roadViewUrl}}" class="btn btn-primary" style="height: 40px;">로드뷰 보기</a>
                        </div>


                    </div>

                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        {{/each}}
    </div>



<script src="/js/lib/jquery.min.js"></script>
<script src="/js/lib/bootstrap.min.js"></script>

<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js" integrity="sha384-w76AqPfDkMBDXo30jS1Sgez6pr3x5MlQ1ZAGC+nuZB+EYdgRZgiwxhTBTkF7CXvN" crossorigin="anonymous"></script>


</body>
</html>